title: What are patients' overall experiences of NHS dentistry care?
analysis_commentary: In 2012/2013, the majority of patients said that they had a very good (47.6%) or fairly good (36.4%) experience of NHS dentistry services. However, there are still over 7% of patients that had a fairly or very poor experience, which translates to over 20,000 patients.
